                <td bgColor="#ECECEC"><textarea cols="48" name="Message" rows="12" wrap="VIRTUAL" onselect="storeCaret(this);" onclick="storeCaret(this);" onkeyup="storeCaret(this);" onchange="storeCaret(this);">[quote][i]Originally posted by xzzy[/i]
[br][quote][i]Originally posted by xxyz[/i]
[br]They are so wrapped up in the game that any insult to an iksar on here would personally offend them, so they desperately try to convince everyone that their choice was the best one.
[/quote]

And that non-iksars are so worried about the small size of their dick that they throw out every counterpoint to their arguments, reasoning it as some unsubstantiated raving from a loser "powergamer".

The "facts" are undeniable. Iksar have better regen and an xp penalty. Everyone else has better int.

It is also a fact that it is much harder to raise regen at high levels than it is int.

It is also a fact that the less HP you lose, the less you have to heal back.


Now whether that makes levelling one race over another significantly different, who the fuck knows, and who the fuck cares. Play what you want.

But to go on some disjointed "iksar necros are mostly powergamers who's entire self worth is based on the race they play" rant because you don't like to hear the above stated facts is a load of bullshit.

People are saying "play iksar" because they get the best regen of any other necro-capabale race. No more, no less. If you can't see the value in that, there's really no reason for you to even be reading this thread because your mind is already made up and nothing is going to change it.

[/quote]</textarea><br /></td>
